<component type="desktop-application">
  <id>com.github.denizsafak.AutoSubSync</id>
  
  <name>AutoSubSync</name>
  <summary>Automatic subtitle synchronization tool</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      AutoSubSync is a user-friendly tool that automatically synchronizes your subtitles with your videos using powerful tools such as ffsubsync, autosubsync, and alass.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Automatic subtitle synchronization using multiple algorithms (ffsubsync, autosubsync, alass)</li>
      <li>Manual subtitle time adjustment</li>
      <li>Batch processing of multiple video-subtitle pairs</li>
      <li>Support for 10+ subtitle formats (SRT, VTT, ASS, SSA, and more)</li>
      <li>Drag-and-drop interface</li>
      <li>23 interface languages</li>
      <li>Sync tracking to avoid re-processing videos</li>
      <li>Library manager for quick access to media folders</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
